'''Lørenskog Ishall''' is an indoor [[Ice hockey rink|ice hockey arena]] located in [[Lørenskog]], [[Norway]]. The capacity of the arena is 2,450 and it was opened in 1984.<ref>[http://www.hockey.no/t2.asp?p=61305 Norwegian ice hockey venues] {{webarchive|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5wJrHSWBi?url=http://www.hockey.no/t2.asp?p=61305 |date=2011-02-07 }} at hockey.no</ref> It is the home arena of the [[Lørenskog IK|Lørenskog]] [[ice hockey]] team. A new rink was installed in 2007.

