'''Pavillon des sports Modibo Keita''' is an [[indoor arena|indoor sporting arena]] located in [[Bamako]], [[Mali]]. The stadium hosted the finals of the 2009 Mali Handball Cup on August 11, 2009. The event was attended by [[Amadou Toumani Touré]], President of the Republic of Mali.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mjsports.gov.ml/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=798&Itemid=1 |title=FINALES DE LA COUPE DU MALI DE HANDBALL : L’Usfas et la Commune II se partagent la poire |date=12-08-2009 |language=French |publisher=Ministere de la Jeunesse et de Sports |accessdate=2009-08-21}}</ref>
